### Next.js sayfalarını HTTP üzerinden doğrula
# Dashboard auth bypass için apps/web/.env.local içine
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_MIDDLEWARE_ENABLED=false

### Ana sayfa
GET {{web}}/

###

### Login sayfası
GET {{web}}/login

###

### Product family sayfaları — hepsi /products/<id>
GET {{web}}/products/one

###

GET {{web}}/products/studio

###

GET {{web}}/products/service

###

GET {{web}}/products/web

###

GET {{web}}/products/mobile

###

GET {{web}}/products/data

###

GET {{web}}/products/intelligence

###

GET {{web}}/products/nexus-code

###

### Storybook (apps/storybook)
GET http://localhost:6006/

###
